snippet.title: Private Eye - Demo Teaser
snippet.description: An snippet of what will be playable on the Oculus Share platform very soon.  Again, not showing off too much as want people to play without knowing what to expect but hopefully gives you an idea of what is to come.  Sorry for the continued delays but day job has gone into overdrive leaving little time to work on Private Eye
